{
  "texts": [
    "Others have claimed that we should give AI rights or protections, because AI inherently deserves them due to its moralcare status (Akst, 2023).",
    "Not only is this suggestion vague, but it is also pragmatically unlikely.",
    "Politically, it is overwhelmingly unlikely that any law would be passed in which a human being is supposed to be arrested, charged, or serve jail time for abusing a chatbot.",
    "The first politician to suggest it would end their career.",
    "Any political party to support it would lose the electorate."
  ]
}